      "what": "Two-phase commit (prepareEvolution/commitEvolution) with recovery pointers following the 13-harness-patterns documentation. Closed-loop verification with rollback is architecturally sound. Mutation rules (GEPA-inspired) are extensible."
    },
    {
      "file": "src/skill-manager.ts",
      "what": "Clean recursive skill discovery with depth limit (prevents infinite recursion). Frontmatter parsing with multiple fallback strategies. slugify() is correctly implemented."
    },
    {
      "file": "src/tools/task-tools.ts",
      "what": "Consistent use of result.success convention from state.router. Clean separation between task, memory, and model routing tools."
    },
    {
      "file": "src/config.ts",
