      "description": "Fix skill-manager API mismatch: skillManager.getSkills() returns Promise<Skill[]> but callers (core-tools.ts:62, index.ts:207) treat it as Result<{ok, data}>. Also fix readContent() → readSkillContent() which doesn't exist on SkillManager."
    },
    {
      "priority": 2,
      "description": "Fix the safety gate interaction with learnFromUser() in honcho-client.ts — structured trace data should not share the user-message write counter and deduplication hash."
    },
    {
      "priority": 3,
      "description": "Deduplicate FTS5 logic: index.ts has its own fts5Search/fts5Stats while fts5-bridge.ts has identical fts5HttpSearch/fts5HttpStats. Use one source."
